data.description: Regular Remarks - One of Oregon's most unique homes. This 4 bed/2.5 bath home features 2 master suites one up/one down,1st floor office and laundry, vaulted family room with gas fp, open concept kitchen with quartz countertops, Samsung SS appl, soft-close cabinets & a walk in pantry you will fall in love with. Charming window lined sunroom w/fp overlooks a privacy fenced yard w/in-ground pool, patio, hot tub & GORGEOUS gardens full of perennials. Steps from walking/biking trail that leads to both Maumee Bay State Park & Pearson Park. See updates list in MLS!
